\af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 In common English parlance, the term property refers to things or objects such as a house, a land, a car, a table\'85etc. It also refers to the right of ownership of person.}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid15749633\charrsid12875540 
