 However, the term, in its legal usage, refers to the rights a person may have in relation to things or objects that have economic value. The things or objects in relation to which property rights are exercised are }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid15749633\charrsid12875540 called objects}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540  of property. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid15749633\charrsid12875540 
