 by their nature contrary to any presumption of purely precarious enjoyment, they can give rise to a possessory action, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid12588778\charrsid12875540 without}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
