p is composed of the following main elements; 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f3\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'2d\tab}}\pard \ltrpar
\qj \fi-360\li360\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls75\adjustright\rin0\lin360\itap0\pararsid11346195 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 The right to use the object himself (the usus)}{\rtlch\fcs1 
