, perform all the legal transactions to which the thing is susceptible, and to exclude all other persons from participating in the exercise of these rights.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid16266356\charrsid12875540  }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 However, an owner may not possess or exercise all the rights set out above and his   rights may be restricted by law or by an agreement he has made with another person.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 
