n
ed, alienated, or acquired through possession in good faith, occupation. See also Art 1454 and 1455. Furthermore, according to Art 40(3) of FDRE Constitution water resources, which include both surface and underground water, are common property of the peo
ples and state of Ethiopia.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid4528776\charrsid12875540  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
