\af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540  197/2000. However, water shall be private property where it is collected in a man made reservoir, basin or cistern from which}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid4528776\charrsid12875540  it does not flow naturally. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540  Art 1229 of the Civil Code.
