d
 administration of the thing are regulated by the agreements entered in to by the joint owners provided that the agreements are not defective/ invalid/ and are not contrary to mandatory provisions of the Civil Code mentioned above. See Arts 1264, 1265, 12
66, 1267, 1268/2/, 1271 and 1274 of the Civil Code.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid9926871\charrsid12875540 
