\ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 Right of recovery i
s a right of a person to recover a thing sold by an owner from the buyer by paying the price and costs the latter has incurred. See Art 1386 of the Civil Code. In other words, right of recovery is a right where by its beneficiary can force the buyer of a 
thing to sell it to him.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid14842528\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
The right of recovery is intended to keep things within a certain group of persons, such as a family or joint owners. It is intended to keep the thing among persons having a blood relationship because of the economic or social val
ue immovable things have among the society. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid14842528\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
It is also intended to keep a property among persons who have close relationship, in cases of joint owners, and keep strangers out there by securing peace and co-operation. Allowing strangers to acquire a shar
e in a jointly owned thing may create problems in the administration of the thing, as almost all decisions have to be made by majority or unanimous vote of joint owners, which may become very difficult if a person who does not get along with the joint own
ers allowed to acquire a share in such things.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid14842528\charrsid12875540 
