yment of capital and/or labor, which contributes to the general welfare and prosperity of the whole community serves a public purpose and is justifiable.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid12266100\charrsid12875540  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 
