\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid227751\charrsid12875540 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 1.\tab}}\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-420\li420\ri0\widctlpar
\jclisttab\tx420\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls17\ilvl1\adjustright\rin0\lin420\itap0\pararsid11346195 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid227751\charrsid12875540 To}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540  determine as to whether the proposed project serves a public purpose or not as we have seen in the preceding secti
on. The competent authorities that are authorized by law to expropriate private property make the determination or declaration of public purpose. The competent authorities may hold, where it appears necessary, a public inquiry as to whether the proposed p
roject serves public purpose.  See Arts 1463 and 1465 of the code.  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid227751\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 2.\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
According Article 1466, after the declaration of public interest, the competent authority shall determine the land required for the implementation of the project, and personal notice sh
all be given to the owners, bare owners, usufructuaries of the immovable he intended expropriation. They are entitled to express their views on the necessity of such expropriation }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid227751\charrsid12875540 
within}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540  a reasonable period of time. Where there is no opposition or the oppo
sition is not accepted, the competent authorities shall make or issue the expropriation order. The order shall transfer the ownership and other rights on the immovable, free of any charge o r encumberance, to the competent authority concerned. Art 1467 of
 the code. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid227751\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}\pard \ltrpar
\qj \fi-360\li360\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls126\adjustright\rin0\lin360\itap0\pararsid11346195 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
Expropriation orders, issued by the competent authorities, must be served on the owner of the immovable and other persons, if any, whose rights on the immovable are entered in the register of the immovable to be expropriated, i.e., the dominan
t owners who have servitude rights over the immovable, the usufractuary, the mortgagee, lessee\'85etc. See Art 1468 of the code.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid227751\charrsid12875540  
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
The person whose property right is affected by the expropriation shall notify the competent authority the amount of 
compensation he claims for such rights with in a period of one month from the date of service of the order. However, any interested person, such as a creditor, may object to the amount of compensation fixed below a certain amount or may oppose the payment
 of compensation in fraud of his rights. This opposition or objection shall be made }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid227751\charrsid12875540 within}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
 the period of one month from the date of service of the order. See Arts 1470 & 1471 of the code.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid227751\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
If the competent authority does not agree with the amount of compen
sation claimed by the person entitled, the amount to be paid shall be fixed the Arbitration Appraisement Committee, which shall be constituted according to rules to be enacted. /Art 1472 and 1473/1/ of the code.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid357957\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
The committee will have the duty to fix th
e amounts of compensation but it cannot decide on disputes regarding the right giving rise to compensation. The amount of compensation or the value of replacement land shall be equal to the actual damage, which shall be assessed on the day when it makes t
h
e decision. See Arts 1473-1474 of the code.The committee shall take in to account, in fixing the amount of compensation or the value of the land to be given replacement of the expropriated land, the claim or statement made by interested parties regarding 
t
he value of the properties or rights to be expropriated, and the increase of the value of the property as a result of construction of public works in the area. However, the committee shall not take in to consideration any improvement or buildings on the l
and, which are made after the service of the expropriation order and any speculation of increase in the value the immovable resulting from the proposed public work. See Art1475 and 1476 of the code.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid357957\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
The competent authority or/and the person who is entitled to payment of compensation may appeal to a court, with in a period of three months from date of service of the decision of the committee, against such decision. See Art 1477 of the code.}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid357957\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
The authority shall take possession of the land only after paying
 the compensation. In case of appeal by the person entitled to the compensation against the amount fixed by the committee, it shall take possession of the immovable only after it has paid the fixed amount to the owner. See Arts 1478/1 & 2/ of the code. Th
e court may not reduce the amount of compensation fixed by the committee. Where the court increases the amount of compensation, the competent authorities shall pay the additional amount. See Art 1478/3/ of the code.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid357957\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
Where the expropriated person is to be given a replacement land, with or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid357957\charrsid12875540 without}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
 monetary compensation, the competent authority shall take possession of the land only after it hands over such land to the person. Where the appeal is ledged by the authority, the owner shall remain in possession o
f the land until the court gives the decision. If the decision is not given with in a period of one year from the date of appeal and compensation is not paid, the expropriation order shall be invalid and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid4745207\charrsid12875540 the owner is not required to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540  comply with it. See Art 1478/4/ of the code.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid357957\charrsid12875540 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f10\fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 \loch\af10\dbch\af0\hich\f10 \'fc\tab}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 
The court may increase the amount of compensation or order payment of additional compensation, in cash in case the owner was given replacement land. Such additional payment has to be made }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
\fs28\insrsid357957\charrsid12875540 within}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540  a period of one month from the date of judgment. See Arts 1478-1479 of the code.
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\s4\qj \li0\ri0\keepn\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel3\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11346195 \rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af0\afs28\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 
