\ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid2119398\charrsid12875540 Where the property to be expropriated is located in rural areas, the compensation to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid11346195\charrsid12875540  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 
