stem of registration a person who intends to buy or secure his rights with mortgage will not be able know whether the person he is dealing with an actual owner and runs the risk of dispossession or eviction or inability to enforce his mortgage. See Arts 2
884 and 3049 of the Civil Code.   }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs28\insrsid11346195\charrsid12875540 
